00:14:13.230 --> 00:14:16.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[dramatic music]</b></Default>

c0000330
00:14:16.230 --> 00:14:23.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000331
00:14:37.590 --> 00:14:39.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both breathing heavily]</b></Default>

c0000332
00:14:39.960 --> 00:14:42.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- My legs!
- Wait, aren't you a first-year?</b></Default>

c0000333
00:14:42.510 --> 00:14:44.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What does that have
to do with anything?</b></Default>

c0000334
00:14:44.090 --> 00:14:45.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both clapping]</b></Default>

c0000335
00:14:48.640 --> 00:14:50.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- These wooden plaques are good
for couples.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:14:50.680 --> 00:14:52.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's fill one out.
- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000337
00:14:52.430 --> 00:14:54.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're really going
to lie to the gods?</b></Default>

c0000338
00:14:54.640 --> 00:14:55.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>S--Stop!</b></Default>

c0000339
00:14:55.980 --> 00:14:57.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's sinful, you know?</b></Default>

c0000340
00:14:57.730 --> 00:14:59.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We should have been prepared
to go to hell once we decided</b></Default>

c0000341
00:14:59.900 --> 00:15:01.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to lie to everyone
at school about us.</b></Default>

c0000342
00:15:02.360 --> 00:15:03.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your turn.
- [whimpers]</b></Default>

c0000343
00:15:03.530 --> 00:15:06.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cicadas chirping]</b></Default>

c0000344
00:15:09.080 --> 00:15:10.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, I'm fine with it,
but...</b></Default>

c0000345
00:15:10.700 --> 00:15:12.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[marker squeaking]</b></Default>

c0000346
00:15:13.290 --> 00:15:14.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

c0000347
00:15:14.960 --> 00:15:16.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>W--Wait a minute!</b></Default>

c0000348
00:15:16.670 --> 00:15:19.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you put a lie in the middle
of everyone's real wishes,</b></Default>

c0000349
00:15:19.210 --> 00:15:20.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that's asking for trouble!</b></Default>

c0000350
00:15:20.550 --> 00:15:22.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll take it home with me.</b></Default>

c0000351
00:15:22.210 --> 00:15:23.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm the only one
that's lying here</b></Default>

c0000352
00:15:23.880 --> 00:15:25.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so it's fine.
Don't worry.</b></Default>

c0000353
00:15:25.300 --> 00:15:26.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000354
00:15:29.390 --> 00:15:31.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta?
- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000355
00:15:31.100 --> 00:15:32.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- About earlier.</b></Default>

c0000356
00:15:33.600 --> 00:15:34.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]
Never mind.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:15:35.810 --> 00:15:37.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've got an idea.</b></Default>

c0000358
00:15:37.350 --> 00:15:39.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think we should go
to the beach now.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:15:39.400 --> 00:15:41.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did put on a swimsuit,
after all.</b></Default>

c0000360
00:15:43.070 --> 00:15:44.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You hear me?</b></Default>

c0000361
00:15:44.400 --> 00:15:46.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Koga.
Enough with the lies.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:15:46.740 --> 00:15:48.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh? Well, yeah.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:15:48.610 --> 00:15:50.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's the last day.
- That's not it.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:15:50.660 --> 00:15:53.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh, you look kinda scary
right now.</b></Default>

c0000365
00:15:53.540 --> 00:15:55.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
- What?</b></Default>

c0000366
00:15:55.410 --> 00:15:56.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's the matter?</b></Default>

c0000367
00:15:57.040 --> 00:15:59.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You seriously thought
I wouldn't notice?</b></Default>

c0000368
00:15:59.170 --> 00:16:01.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I have no idea what
you're talking about.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:16:01.380 --> 00:16:02.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Even if it was a lie,</b></Default>

c0000370
00:16:02.840 --> 00:16:04.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was your boyfriend
for three weeks.</b></Default>

c0000371
00:16:05.840 --> 00:16:08.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm someone who can take hints.
I just choose not to.</b></Default>

c0000372
00:16:11.300 --> 00:16:13.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But if you don't wanna say it,
I will.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:16:14.720 --> 00:16:16.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No matter how many times
you keep re-rolling,</b></Default>

c0000374
00:16:17.060 --> 00:16:19.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it won't change feelings.</b></Default>

c0000375
00:16:19.230 --> 00:16:23.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lies won't become reality,
and reality won't become lies.</b></Default>

c0000376
00:16:24.940 --> 00:16:27.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Not after 100 times?
- No.</b></Default>

c0000377
00:16:27.700 --> 00:16:30.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Or 1,000 times?
- That's right.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:16:30.450 --> 00:16:31.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- 10,000 times?</b></Default>

c0000379
00:16:31.990 --> 00:16:33.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It could be 100 million times.</b></Default>

c0000380
00:16:34.490 --> 00:16:36.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll always be in love with Mai.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:16:36.910 --> 00:16:40.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can repeat the same thing
but feelings stay in stasis.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:16:48.550 --> 00:16:50.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm sorry, Sakuta,
but you're wrong.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:16:50.800 --> 00:16:52.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Feelings can be changed.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:16:53.300 --> 00:16:55.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They keep building up
the more you repeat them.</b></Default>

c0000385
00:16:55.970 --> 00:16:57.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just like they have for me.</b></Default>

c0000386
00:16:59.190 --> 00:17:03.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I tried to forget but couldn't
no matter how hard I tried.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:17:03.610 --> 00:17:06.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I even thought this time
I'll do it for sure.</b></Default>

c0000388
00:17:07.110 --> 00:17:10.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to say goodbye
to these feelings so badly.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:17:10.280 --> 00:17:12.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales]
Today you and I are supposed</b></Default>

c0000390
00:17:12.910 --> 00:17:15.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to have our last really
fun date together.</b></Default>

c0000391
00:17:15.790 --> 00:17:19.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going to end this fake
relationship with a big smile.</b></Default>

c0000392
00:17:19.710 --> 00:17:21.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're gonna be free
to go hit it off</b></Default>

c0000393
00:17:21.460 --> 00:17:23.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with Sakurajima like you wanted.</b></Default>

c0000394
00:17:23.500 --> 00:17:25.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then in the second term
I'll poke fun at you</b></Default>

c0000395
00:17:25.800 --> 00:17:27.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by saying something like,
"Wow, you actually did it.</b></Default>

c0000396
00:17:27.920 --> 00:17:29.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good for you."</b></Default>

c0000397
00:17:29.760 --> 00:17:31.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And eventually we're
gonna become friends.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:17:32.510 --> 00:17:34.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good friends that
can talk about anything.</b></Default>

c0000399
00:17:34.890 --> 00:17:37.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll be the older one
who spoils me sometimes.</b></Default>

c0000400
00:17:37.470 --> 00:17:39.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One day we'll look back on today
and be like,</b></Default>

c0000401
00:17:39.890 --> 00:17:41.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Remember when we pretended
to date?</b></Default>

c0000402
00:17:41.560 --> 00:17:43.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was pretty fun, wasn't it?"</b></Default>

c0000403
00:17:43.350 --> 00:17:45.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And we'll laugh about it
and be best friends forever.</b></Default>

c0000404
00:17:47.110 --> 00:17:48.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll be best friends.</b></Default>

c0000405
00:17:49.820 --> 00:17:51.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's the only thing
I'm wishing for.</b></Default>

c0000406
00:17:52.700 --> 00:17:55.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not like I wanted anything
that special.</b></Default>

c0000407
00:17:55.370 --> 00:17:57.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wasn't being selfish.</b></Default>

c0000408
00:17:57.740 --> 00:17:59.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I wasn't really even
troubling anyone else.</b></Default>

c0000409
00:18:00.660 --> 00:18:01.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So why?</b></Default>

c0000410
00:18:02.580 --> 00:18:03.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why?</b></Default>

c0000411
00:18:04.790 --> 00:18:07.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why is it tomorrow won't come
for me already?</b></Default>

c0000412
00:18:07.170 --> 00:18:09.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why do my feeling continue
to grow each time</b></Default>

c0000413
00:18:09.460 --> 00:18:10.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wake up in the morning?</b></Default>

c0000414
00:18:10.880 --> 00:18:12.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's all such torture.</b></Default>

c0000415
00:18:12.720 --> 00:18:15.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I decided to pretend
that none of it happened.</b></Default>

c0000416
00:18:15.550 --> 00:18:16.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You don't have to do that,
Koga.</b></Default>

c0000417
00:18:17.050 --> 00:18:18.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I do have to!</b></Default>

c0000418
00:18:18.350 --> 00:18:19.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's because I know how madly</b></Default>

c0000419
00:18:19.890 --> 00:18:21.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in love you are with Sakurajima.</b></Default>

c0000420
00:18:21.680 --> 00:18:23.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd just inconvenience you!</b></Default>

c0000421
00:18:23.640 --> 00:18:26.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not supposed
to feel this way about a friend.</b></Default>

c0000422
00:18:26.520 --> 00:18:28.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>These feelings shouldn't exist
between friends!</b></Default>

c0000423
00:18:28.860 --> 00:18:30.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Did I ever say that I
was inconvenienced?</b></Default>

c0000424
00:18:30.990 --> 00:18:32.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000425
00:18:32.530 --> 00:18:33.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's cruel.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:18:34.360 --> 00:18:36.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hate you so much, Sakuta!
You're the worst!</b></Default>

c0000427
00:18:36.870 --> 00:18:38.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is all your fault!</b></Default>

c0000428
00:18:38.450 --> 00:18:40.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's 'cause you were always
so nice to me!</b></Default>

c0000429
00:18:40.330 --> 00:18:41.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Let it all out.</b></Default>

c0000430
00:18:41.910 --> 00:18:44.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't have to worry about
being considerate of me.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:18:44.580 --> 00:18:46.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I hate myself
so much right now.</b></Default>

c0000432
00:18:46.750 --> 00:18:48.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This isn't me!</b></Default>

c0000433
00:18:48.170 --> 00:18:49.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're wrong, Koga.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:18:49.340 --> 00:18:50.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is part of you.</b></Default>

c0000435
00:18:50.550 --> 00:18:51.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's not!</b></Default>

c0000436
00:18:51.760 --> 00:18:53.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is nothing like me!</b></Default>

c0000437
00:18:53.340 --> 00:18:55.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really want summer break
to get here.</b></Default>

c0000438
00:18:55.590 --> 00:18:58.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanna hurry and become friends
with you so we can have fun!</b></Default>

c0000439
00:18:58.550 --> 00:19:00.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's my greatest wish!</b></Default>

c0000440
00:19:00.220 --> 00:19:02.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You don't need to keep lying
to yourself anymore.</b></Default>

c0000441
00:19:02.520 --> 00:19:03.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000442
00:19:04.770 --> 00:19:07.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're a high school
girl fighting for justice.</b></Default>

c0000443
00:19:07.310 --> 00:19:08.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's nothing you're
not capable of.</b></Default>

c0000444
00:19:09.070 --> 00:19:10.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's cheating.</b></Default>

c0000445
00:19:10.440 --> 00:19:12.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's so unfair to put
it that way.</b></Default>

c0000446
00:19:13.360 --> 00:19:14.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's okay.</b></Default>

c0000447
00:19:14.780 --> 00:19:16.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can stop holding back now.</b></Default>

c0000448
00:19:16.700 --> 00:19:18.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [whimpering]</b></Default>

c0000449
00:19:19.030 --> 00:19:23.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're a big idiot and I--
I hate you!</b></Default>

c0000450
00:19:23.450 --> 00:19:25.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And yet, I...</b></Default>

c0000451
00:19:27.170 --> 00:19:28.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm...</b></Default>

c0000452
00:19:29.540 --> 00:19:31.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm in love with you, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000453
00:19:32.210 --> 00:19:33.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000454
00:19:33.380 --> 00:19:37.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I love you!</b></Default>

c0000455
00:19:41.140 --> 00:19:43.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Koga, you tried so hard.</b></Default>

c0000456
00:19:43.640 --> 00:19:44.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [whimpers]</b></Default>

c0000457
00:19:45.270 --> 00:19:46.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You gave it your best.</b></Default>

c0000458
00:19:47.140 --> 00:19:50.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [crying]</b></Default>

c0000459
00:19:59.910 --> 00:20:02.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000460
00:20:02.620 --> 00:20:04.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And the Japanese team
has won their match.</b></Default>

c0000461
00:20:05.410 --> 00:20:06.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good morning, everyone.
- [meows]</b></Default>

c0000462
00:20:06.500 --> 00:20:08.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Today is Friday, June 27th.</b></Default>

c0000463
00:20:08.710 --> 00:20:10.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- Let's begin our segment...</b></Default>

c0000464
00:20:10.670 --> 00:20:13.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She really is incredible.
- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000465
00:20:13.960 --> 00:20:16.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It was all just a simulation
of the future</b></Default>

c0000466
00:20:16.340 --> 00:20:17.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from the very start.</b></Default>

c0000467
00:20:17.720 --> 00:20:18.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- When Japan landed that goal,</b></Default>

c0000468
00:20:18.720 --> 00:20:19.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I jumped out of my seat.</b></Default>

c0000469
00:20:21.220 --> 00:20:23.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, Mai.
- What is it?</b></Default>

c0000470
00:20:24.140 --> 00:20:26.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I love you.
- Please go out with me.</b></Default>

c0000471
00:20:28.020 --> 00:20:29.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- When you hear the same thing
for a whole month,</b></Default>

c0000472
00:20:29.980 --> 00:20:32.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it stops making your heart race.
It's less charming.</b></Default>

c0000473
00:20:32.650 --> 00:20:35.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I see. Got turned down.</b></Default>

c0000474
00:20:35.150 --> 00:20:37.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess I'll just have
to look for a new romance, then.</b></Default>

c0000475
00:20:37.450 --> 00:20:38.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Wait, what?</b></Default>

c0000476
00:20:38.900 --> 00:20:41.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Thank you for everything
up until now.</b></Default>

c0000477
00:20:41.200 --> 00:20:43.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I didn't exactly say no.</b></Default>

c0000478
00:20:43.160 --> 00:20:45.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why are you giving up so easily?</b></Default>

c0000479
00:20:45.120 --> 00:20:46.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So, will you?</b></Default>

c0000480
00:20:46.790 --> 00:20:48.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000481
00:20:48.910 --> 00:20:50.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is so forward of you,
Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000482
00:20:50.790 --> 00:20:51.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Will you?</b></Default>

c0000483
00:20:53.340 --> 00:20:55.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
Yeah, I will.</b></Default>

c0000484
00:20:57.920 --> 00:21:01.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So Mai, would you mind if I
ask you how you feel about me?</b></Default>

c0000485
00:21:01.090 --> 00:21:03.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- About you?
Well, I--</b></Default>

c0000486
00:21:03.550 --> 00:21:04.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You what?
- I don't think</b></Default>

c0000487
00:21:04.970 --> 00:21:06.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it really matters.
- I wouldn't be asking you</b></Default>

c0000488
00:21:06.890 --> 00:21:08.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if that were true.</b></Default>

c0000489
00:21:08.770 --> 00:21:10.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You really want me
to tell you?</b></Default>

c0000490
00:21:10.310 --> 00:21:11.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes.</b></Default>

c0000491
00:21:12.150 --> 00:21:13.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Look!
- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000492
00:21:20.200 --> 00:21:21.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You understand now,
don't you?</b></Default>

c0000493
